Paper: 10121692
Title: Consistent Levi Civita truncation uniquely characterizes the Lovelock  Lagrangians
Authors: Naresh Dadhich and Josep M. Pons
Abstract: We define the concept of Levi Civita truncation for a Lagrangian in the Palatini formulation with an arbitrary connection, and show that its consistency uniquely identifies the Lovelock Lagrangians.
